name: I Catch Killers with Gary Jubelin

episodes.title: Bringing Down The Predator Malka Leifer (Part 2) | I Catch Killers Podcast
episodes.description:
Nicole Meyer was first abused by her school principal when she was 15 years old. Malka Leifer continued abusing her, and her sisters - Dassi Erlich and Elly Sapper - for years. From grooming the community to breaking off Nicole’s engagement, Leifer controlled every aspect of her life. The sisters finally broke their silence, reporting the rapist to police. But, in the middle of one night in 2008, Leifer fled the country.

Watch the Stan Original documentary, Surviving Malka Leifer, out October 5.
